message.body: Second half of assessment not as exciting as the first. Got a game plan tho. Let me know when u want to do the walk thru.
When's good? After work would be easiest for me, pretty much any day next week
After work works for me. How about Wed?
Sounds good! Do you want to schedule it or should I?
I can. What time? 5? Do you want to plan to do a lil workout after our walk through?
I could do 5. Maybe we could do some swimming after the walk through? I think the loop has open stunning at 6
I'm game for either... Stunning or Swimming !
Will 5:30 on Wed work for u?
Well I guess I sort of already made the 5:30 appointment so if it doesn't work let me know and I'll change it.
Nope, that's fine! Sorry, was at lunch :-)
